title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS TOYOTA LANDCRUISER 70 SERIES (2007+) FUEL MANAGER PRE-FILTER KIT INCL. DUAL BRACKET

content.rendered:
WESTERN FILTERS TOYOTA LANDCRUISER 70 SERIES (2007+) FUEL MANAGER PRE-FILTER KIT INCL. DUAL BRACKET

Western Filters Toyota Landcruiser 70 Series (2007+) Fuel Manager Pre-filter Kit including Dual Bracket available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Fuel Manager Pre Filter / Water Separator Kit for:

  • Toyota Landcruiser 70 Series (2007-on)
  • 4.5L V8 Turbo Diesel VDJ76/78/79 1VD-FTV DOHC 32V
  • BOTH Single & Dual battery models

This kit fits directly onto our Provent Catch Can kit using the same bracket, utilising one bracket for two very important uses and protecting your vehicle! This Fuel Water Separator kit will not cause flow restriction as it is capable of 114 lph of fuel flow.

Contaminated fuel can lead to vehicle downtime and costly repairs, especially to expensive common rail systems and components. Modern engines are increasingly requiring better fuel filtration technology to ensure delivery of the cleanest fuel to your vehicle’s fuel system.

Kit OS-30-FMB Contents:

  • Western Filters Dual Bracket for Toyota LC70s
  • 1x FM Fuel Filtration Unit
  • Hoses
  • Fittings
  • Hose Clamps
  • Thread Sealant

T check out the full range of products available for your Landcruiser, CLICK HERE!
